":"2021-02-08T12:33:08.000Z","msg":"求香港移民定東方移民？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6a77ec0e444e8cf68bb0098acb3b3aeaed1831","tid":2399204,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:57:32.000Z","msg":"食好住好屌得好 係下下簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那人咩思想"},{"pid":"95fc31d2ecf5847cd94179c058814cf97b1f3cfd","tid":2399204,"uid":62226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:59:42.000Z","msg":"東方創辦人都係出名移民移得好"},{"pid":"9d510c9d1c7dcdf75783bbef3dd7e15c2fbe7f1d","tid":2399204,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:00:09.000Z","msg":"手足解讀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#288 Lollipoppy<br />\n<blockquote>其實求籤睇相算命嗰啲 遷移不嬲唔係好事<br />\n畢竟古代啲人係唔搬先係好<br />\n佢講咩下下籤 大凶咩<br />\n係可以用移民應咗個劫佢<br />\n<br />\n就好似呢支籤咁<br />\n所有嘢都好差 唯獨for移民係好正面 叫大家快撚啲走<br />\n<br />\n如果佢吹話求到上上籤 都可以解讀成一切順利 唔駛擔心<br />\n即係呢種故事係唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n#288 - 東 方 日 報 ： 移 民 冇 好 下 場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/spdOLmX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/spdOLmX</a><br />\n<br />\n黃 大 仙 ： 香 港 人 快 快 移 民 ！ 做 太 空 人 冇 好 下 場 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2399679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2399679</a>"},{"pid":"e2d94aae4be1c3ee814f7eb1c167fbd081f9e49d","tid":2399204,"uid":293937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3856e0165fe9f8666fc1c70816c8093b887a576","tid":2399204,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:31:29.000Z","msg":"老共最唔希望香港人移民賣資產<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少左錢又少左奴隸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:06:04.000Z","msg":"冇左有錢韭菜比習近平割"}]}